title: HOUR 3- Derrick Henry Oct 15, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Derrick Henry Oct 15, 2020
description:
Derrick Henry tells Dan that he was too busy paying attention to the results of his stiff arm on Josh Norman; that he didn't realize that he was running out of bounds. Derrick says by the time he realized it, he was on the sidelines besides his team mates.
